00:21:11.770 --> 00:21:15.540
Monaka semakin hampir,
jadi mari kita cepatkan rentak, Daifuku.

00:21:15.607 --> 00:21:17.042
Pergi, Daifuku!

00:21:17.109 --> 00:21:20.212
Monaka sudah biasa
berjalan betul-betul di belakang Daifuku.

